Class InCodeExperimentDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.artisan.incodeapi.ExperimentDetails
      • com.artisan.incodeapi.InCodeExperimentDetails

  • public class InCodeExperimentDetails
extends ExperimentDetails
    An object containing useful information about an in-code experiment.

    These are retrieved via the `ArtisanExperimentManager#getInCodeExperimentDetails` method
